short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: For those who enjoy the dark side of life

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Embrace the darkness.Turn your new tab into a source of motivation and inspiration combined with dark aesthetic imagery from Unsplash. Our mission is to welcome you with a new inspirational quote with a dark aesthetic theme every time you change your tab. We want to make your Chrome New Tab an ultimate source of inspiration. The extension comes with some of the darkest yet most inspirational quotes from the best of the best teachers in the world whose writing revolves around peace and mindfulness.

By clicking "add to Chrome", I accept and agree to installing the Dark Home Tab extension and setting Chrome New Tab search provider to Microsoft Bing as described by the service in the Terms of Use https://dark-home-page.com/terms-conditions/ and Policy https://dark-home-page.com/privacy-policy/
